{"TopicId":115755,"ForumId":18,"TopicTitle":"Satoru Iwata, president of Nintendo, has passed away","CreatedByName":"SkyRender","CreatedById":10651,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-07-13T00:33:59Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"SkyRender","CreatedById":10651,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-07-13T00:33:59Z","Content":"\n\u003Ca href=\u0022http://www.nintendo.co.jp/ir/pdf/2015/150713e.pdf\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003EIn a brief press release\u003C/a\u003E, Nintendo has revealed that the president of the company, Satoru Iwata, passed away yesterday due to complications involving a growth in his bile duct. He will be missed.\n"},{"CreatedByName":"HoloYolo","CreatedById":138353,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-07-13T00:39:13Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EThat sucks. RIP in pepperoni Satoru Iwata.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Alshain","CreatedById":110959,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-07-13T00:57:41Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EI\u0027m so sorry to hear this. Next to the PC, Nintendo makes my favorite gaming systems.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"mythbusters844","CreatedById":72313,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-07-13T01:03:20Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EWow, that\u0027s saddening \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_sad.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:(\u0022\u003E. My condolences to his family and friends.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Kaboom!\u0022 data-cite=\u0022Kaboom!\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003ERIP in pepperoni Satoru Iwata.\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003EHow hilarious, original, and respectful.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"HoloYolo","CreatedById":138353,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-07-13T01:07:42Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022mythbusters844\u0022 data-cite=\u0022mythbusters844\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003EWow, that\u0027s saddening \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_sad.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:(\u0022\u003E. My condolences to his family and friends.\u003Cp\u003EHow hilarious, original, and respectful.\u003C/p\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003EI really do feel bad, it\u0027s a joke to try to brighten the mood. Deathes are sad, no matter who you are or what you did.\n"},{"CreatedByName":"kenbobo","CreatedById":70629,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-07-13T16:09:11Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EFarewell.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E(and this is not meant to be a joke, but as my sign of respect.)\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsEmbeddedVideo\u0022 contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003E\u003Ciframe width=\u0022480\u0022 height=\u0022270\u0022 src=\u0022https://www.youtube.com/embed/s2-zTspthXw?feature=oembed\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 allowfullscreen=\u0022true\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"pxi","CreatedById":78711,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-07-13T18:15:44Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:12px;\u0022\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:10px;\u0022\u003E\u00C3\u00A2\u00E2\u201A\u00AC\u00C5\u201COn my business card, I am a corporate president. In my mind, I am a game developer. But in my heart, I am a gamer.\u00C3\u00A2\u00E2\u201A\u00AC\u00C2\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:12px;\u0022\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:10px;\u0022\u003E\u00C3\u00A2\u00E2\u201A\u00AC\u00E2\u20ACSatoru Iwata \u003C/span\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003ERIP Iwata-san\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Rainbowtrout","CreatedById":60253,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-07-13T19:46:39Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EI played a lot of Nintendo games when I was younger. RIP Iwata.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"windows_x_seven","CreatedById":112926,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-07-14T